ugh each plaque-\n\ntte in the top (bottom) layer (See Fig. 1).\n\n2. Optically Implementing the Interlayer Tunneling\n\nThe inter-layer hopping term is relatively straightfor-\n\nward.", "embedding": [0.0020863137, -0.014755536, -0.019199587, -0.008256744, -0.010200313, -0.00988613, -0.015121839, -0.023219373, -0.06162657, 0.10182673, 0.010482919, -0.024659723, 0.010318502, -0.070430875, -0.0025678568, 0.015869066, -0.014206878, 0.006420146, -0.07537712, -0.006933654, 0.013771058, -0.017991237, -0.051594008, -0.019284915, -0.04230486, 0.037296712, -0.012676852, 0.013483851, 0.05119054, 0.04991295, 0.039900906, -0.04346414, 0.020355733, -0.045749396, -0.01707948, 0.019219233, -0.0015828331, -0.01382973, 0.027213302, -0.021255687, 0.04776691, -0.0068148705, 0.018808838, -0.010425911, -0.011743257, -0.021758653, -0.040572222, -0.034449693, -0.019025903, -0.078697085, -0.010465398, 0.022673562, 0.0366965, 0.02257614, -0.004846815, -0.0035227155, -0.014140195, -0.026757201, -0.0041023786, -0.005931713, 0.031064922, -0.029007217, 0.027730668, -0.06221887, 0.027166417, 0.056933522, -0.0012247112, 0.06797241, -0.04217947, -0.03942068, -0.027660258, -0.009851451, -0.006998666, 0.0012343031, -0.028533995, 0.03319114, -0.011511791, -0.03446276, -0.07626401, -0.0006556012, -0.005516857, -0.04113755, -0.027077489, 0.03251753, 0.02573338, 0.006059006, 0.0022457298, -0.021499148, -0.009290782, 0.0015363069, 0.042365372, 0.06808414, -0.013513043, -0.025753645, 0.0031708863, 0.021847958, -0.006336816, 0.030261783, 0.042516544, 0.025934884, -0.008560189, 0.053472724, -0.027885603, 0.029126566, -0.03214127, 0.008419217, -0.0150671005, -0.0037561217, -0.01156517, -0.039264437, -0.020285575, -0.0036369506, 0.0021713164, 0.03652235, 0.013940438, 0.039668325, -0.00012512632, 0.01164273, -0.021685593, 0.005648588, -0.003226316, -0.035237715, 0.051128063, 0.05677879, -0.022558995, -0.012650187, -0.027225535, 0.029276893, -0.035376776, -0.023232473, 0.013348368, 0.0009387488, 0.013338579, 0